text: Novy Kalkash () is a rural locality (a village) in Starokalkashevsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 226 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 15 km from Sterlibashevo, 3 km from Stary Kalkash. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Novy Kalkash
